<h2>The Three-Tier Ownership Framework</h2>
<p>Understanding AI copyright content ownership requires sorting your content into three categories. Each category carries different legal protections and different risks.</p>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Tier</th>
<th>Description</th>
<th>Copyright Status</th>
<th>Example</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
